msgid ""
"K3b was created to be a feature-rich and easy to handle CD burning "
"application. It consists of basically three parts:"
msgstr ""
"K3b schall en eenfach bruukbor CD-Brennprogramm mit vele Funkschonen wesen. "
"Dat is in de Hööftsaak ut dree Delen opbuut:"

